WEBVTT

00:03:58.987 --> 00:04:01.387
tulibidi kuchunguza mwili mzima,

00:04:01.411 --> 00:04:04.498
kisha tulibudi kuchimba ndani zaidi katika viungo,

00:04:04.522 --> 00:04:05.855
katika tishu,

00:04:05.879 --> 00:04:07.381
kote hadi kwa seli mojamoja,

00:04:07.405 --> 00:04:09.742
ili tunaweza kuchunguza vizuri.

00:04:10.762 --> 00:04:13.593
Hivyo kwa maagizo ya Rais mwenyewe,

00:04:13.617 --> 00:04:16.730
tulianza na njia halisi kabisa ya kisayansi:

00:04:16.754 --> 00:04:17.929
kukusanya data

00:04:17.953 --> 00:04:20.040
data zote tulizoweza kupata--

00:04:20.064 --> 00:04:21.321
kuunda nadharia,

00:04:21.345 --> 00:04:22.582
kutafuta ufumbuzi,

00:04:22.606 --> 00:04:23.798
mmoja baada nyingine.

00:04:24.845 --> 00:04:28.880
Hivyo tulikutana na mamia ya watu waliofanya kazi katika mashirika ya serikali,

00:04:28.904 --> 00:04:32.840
kuanzia vyombo vya kodi, ardhi, kampuni za huduma,